 border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color=
: #ccc;">tweeted this</a>:</p><blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Toda=
y I=E2=80=99m investigating Twitter for potentially misleading Texans on th=
e number of its =E2=80=9Cbot=E2=80=9D users. I have a duty to protect Texan=
s if Twitter is misrepresenting how many accounts are fake to drive up thei=
