ir trading screens. Goldman Sachs registered that on some days less than $2=
mn worth of the contracts could be bought or sold at the price actively quo=
ted in the market, the lowest level since March 2020.</p></blockquote><p st=
yle=3D"margin: 16px 0;">I kind of feel like we=E2=80=99re stuck with algori=
